text: Came in for Tuesday lunch on a business trip, not too busy and good service. They have a $6 lunch special and salad bar but no pizza lunch buffet. Seems clean and plenty of windows so it's not too dark. Definitely recommend!

name: Frank Aranda Reviews
text: Very clean place. Great for a night out or family pizza time. Has TVs to watch the games. A lot of seating. Good environment. Customer service could be a bit better. But I think the salad bar compensates for that. Decent establishment overall.
